// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1857 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 91800827-d53d-5ed7-bf60-c442bf16ef9a

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
